OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FA Cumbrian MP has warned children who
OL,7,F'doom scroll' social media content for
OL,8,Fhours a day are at risk of widespread
OL,9,Fharm.
OL,11,FLabour MP for Whitehaven and
OL,12,FWorkington Josh MacAlister believes
OL,13,Fonline addictive content viewed by
OL,14,Fchildren on their smartphones needs to
OL,15,Fbe managed through "seatbelt"
OL,16,Flegislation.
