OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FThe former teacher will introduce a
OL,7,FPrivate Member's Bill on protecting
OL,8,Fchildren from harms caused by
OL,9,Fexcessive screen time in Parliament on
OL,10,F16 October 2024.
OL,12,FThe Bill will call for all schools in
OL,13,FEngland to become mobile-free zones,
OL,14,Fwith the aim to empower families and
OL,15,Fteachers to cut down on children's
OL,16,Fdaily smartphone screen time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
