OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FHe said: "Adults find it hard enough
OL,7,Fto manage screen time, so why are we
OL,8,Fexpecting children to manage this
OL,9,Faddictive content without some shared
OL,10,Frules? Parents are in an impossible
OL,11,Fbind over whether to ostracise their
OL,12,Fchild from social media or expose them
OL,13,Fto the harms and addiction of content.
OL,15,F"Countries around the world are now
OL,16,Ftaking bold action and our children
OL,17,Frisk being left behind. It's time to
OL,18,Fhave the national debate here in the
OL,19,FUK."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
