OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FMPs are expected to debate the issue
OL,7,Fin the new year, Mr MacAlister's
OL,8,Foffice said.
OL,10,FIntending to make smartphones less
OL,11,Faddictive, the Bill is also expected
OL,12,Fto call for companies to change the
OL,13,Fage from which they can gain data
OL,14,Fconsensually from children without
OL,15,Fparental permission from 13 to 16
OL,16,Fyears old.
