OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FOther proposals include strengthening
OL,7,Fwatchdog Ofcom's powers to protect
OL,8,Fchildren from apps that are designed
OL,9,Fto be addictive, and committing the
OL,10,FGovernment to review further
OL,11,Fregulation if needed of the design,
OL,12,Fsupply, marketing and use of mobile
OL,13,Fphones by children under the age of 16.
OL,15,FConservative MP Kit Malthouse, who was
OL,16,FEducation Secretary during Liz Truss's
OL,17,Fpremiership in 2022, says the evidence
OL,18,Fis "deeply alarming".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
