OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F353A1729020967
OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,F"So being clear about our expectations
OL,7,Ffrom providers and regulators, and
OL,8,Ftheir duties towards our children, has
OL,9,Fto be a step in the right direction,
OL,10,Fand I'm pleased to support a Bill that
OL,11,Fdoes exactly that."
OL,13,FPepe Di'lasio, general secretary of
OL,14,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,15,FLeaders (ASCL), said: "Smartphones and
OL,16,Fthe instant access they provide to
OL,17,Fharmful content is nothing short of a
OL,18,Fpublic health emergency for children
OL,19,Fand young people."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
