OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FHe added: "It is not enough to rely
OL,7,Fsolely on parents and schools teaching
OL,8,Fchildren about the dangers of
OL,9,Fsmartphones. We have reached a point
OL,10,Fwhere regulation is required over
OL,11,Ftheir sale and the conduct of online
OL,12,Fplatforms."
