OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,FJoe Ryrie, co-founder of the
OL,7,FSmartphone Free Childhood campaign
OL,8,Fgroup, said: "Parents everywhere are
OL,9,Fcrying out for the Government to go
OL,10,Ffurther and faster in regulating big
OL,11,Ftech so that they alone are not
OL,12,Fresponsible for guarding childhood
OL,13,Ffrom the addictive and predatory
OL,14,Falgorithms for which they are no match.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
