OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,F"We need to start thinking about
OL,7,Fchildren's digital safety in a more
OL,8,Fimaginative way, going beyond just the
OL,9,Fharms, so that we can build upon the
OL,10,FOnline Safety Act and start developing
OL,11,Fa new regulatory approach that has
OL,12,Fyoung people's wellbeing and healthy
OL,13,Fdevelopment at its heart."
OL,15,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,16,Fall want to find the best way of
OL,17,Fensuring children are kept safe while
OL,18,Falso benefiting from the latest
OL,19,Fdigital technology.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
