OL,3,CCumbrian MP calls for legislation to
OL,4,Cprevent children 'doom scrolling'
OL,6,F"The Online Safety Act will introduce
OL,7,Fstrong safeguards for children,
OL,8,Fpreventing them from accessing harmful
OL,9,Fand age-inappropriate content.
OL,11,F"This will include requiring companies
OL,12,Fto check the age of children so that
OL,13,Fparents can have peace of mind about
OL,14,Fthe safety of their children online.
OL,16,F"The vast majority of schools already
OL,17,Fhandle the use of mobile phones
OL,18,Feffectively, including with bans.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
